<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
    Thank you for using our Natai Diary application. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and share
    information that we collect from you while you use our application.
</p>

<h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>

<p>
    1.1. User Notes: Our diary application collects user notes to enable you to create, store, and manage your diary
